citations:
    citation-agot-arya-iii:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Arya III"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Arya trains with Syrio Forel (First Sword of Braavos) in King's Landing. Syrio's teaching methods: balance on one leg, blindfolded training ('see with ears, nose, skin'), catching cats. Ned watches a Hand's tourney feast. Ned notices Lancel Lannister among Robert's squires. Ned reflects on Gendry (Robert's bastard, apprentice to an armorer) and Robert's other bastards including a daughter in the Vale and a boy at Storm's End being fostered by Lord Renly's castellan."
